The paper discusses the use of controllers for planning, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The concept of hierarchical controllers involves the use of multiple levels of controllers, which is related to programming languages and compilers (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the use of controllers in robotics (cs.RO) and the use of machine learning techniques to generate controllers (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the use of controllers in systems engineering (cs.SY).
